results.deck: Majesco is a North American video game publisher, founded in 1988
results.description: Majesco was founded as Majesco Sales, Inc. and renamed to Majesco Entertainment Company early in 2005. Majesco distributes, develops and publishes games for various platforms, including Nintendo DS, Dreamcast, SNES, PSP and XBOX 360.
